  "text": "Using these properties, in order to analyze NFI, it is enough to consider the functions f k for k ≥ 1. It was shown in [CITATION_1] that the asymptotic approximation ratio of NFI for the function f k (k ≥ 2) is at most 1 + 1 k . The asymptotic approximation ratio of NFI for f 1 , that is, for classic bin packing, follows from the results of [CITATION_2] and from Lemma 1. This ratio is",
